                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>MISCELLANEOUS PROVISIONS<b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.1	SCHEDULES<b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>The Schedules annexed to this Agreement shall be an integral part of this Agreement and shall be read in conjunction with the terms and conditions contained herein.</td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.2	ASSIGNMENT <b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>The Borrower expressly recognizes and accepts that KFI shall be entitled to and has full authority to sell, assign or transfer its rights and obligations under this Agreement to any person(s) of its choice in whole or in part and in such manner and on such terms as KFI may decide. Any such sale, assignment or transfer shall be binding on the Borrower. All Obligations of the Borrower and the Guarantors under this Agreement shall continue to remain in full force vis a vis the prospective transferee/ assignee/purchaser to whom KFI may have sold, assigned or otherwise transferred or licensed in any manner, in whole or in part and on such terms as KFI may decide.The Borrower and/ or the Guarantors shall not be entitled to directly or indirectly assign the Obligations under this Agreement without prior written consent of KFI. </td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.3	INSPECTIONS<b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>KFI may at the risk and cost of the Borrower engage one or more person(s) to verify any facts or information furnished by, concerning or pertaining to the Borrower and/or in relation to this Agreement and/or to collect the Borrower’s Dues and/or to enforce any Security and may furnish to such person(s) such documents, information, facts and figures as KFI thinks fit and may delegate to such person(s) the right and authority to perform and execute all acts, deeds, matters and things connected therewith or incidental thereto as KFI thinks fit.KFI shall be entitled to carry inspections at such intervals as it may deem fit.</td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.4	NOTICES<b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>All notices, requests, demands, waivers and other communications required or permitted to be given under this Agreement shall be in writing and shall be deemed to have been duly given if (a) delivered personally, (b) mailed, certified or registered mail with postage prepaid on the addresses as set out in the Agreement. </td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.5	ARBITRATION AND JURISDICTION<b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>All the disputes or differences arising between the parties hereto as to the interpretation of this Agreement or any covenants or conditions thereof or as to the rights, duties or liabilities of any Party hereunder or as to any act, performance or non-performance of any act, deed or thing as agreed under this agreement or matter or thing arising out of or relating to or under this Agreement (even though the Agreement may have been terminated), the same shall be referred to the arbitration to be governed by the Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996. The Arbitral Tribunal shall consist of a sole arbitrator to be appointed by KFI. The language of arbitration shall be English and the seat of arbitration shall be Pune. The decision of the said Arbitrator shall be final, conclusive and binding upon the Parties hereto. All costs of Arbitration, including the Arbitrator’s fees, advocate’s fees, traveling costs and other miscellaneous expenses shall be borne equally by the Parties hereto. Any dispute relating to this Agreement shall be resolved, decided and/or settled on the   basis of the laws of Indiaand the Courts at Pune to the exclusion of the other Courts shall have exclusive jurisdiction to entertain any dispute.</td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.6	WAIVER<b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>Any delay in exercising or omission to exercise any right, power or remedy accruing to KFI under this Agreement or any other Agreement or document shall not impair any such right, power or remedy and shall not be construed to be a waiver thereof or any acquiescence in any default; nor shall the action or inaction of KFI in respect of any default or any acquiescence by it in any default, affect or impair any right, power or remedy of KFI in respect of any other default.</td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.7	INDEMNITY<b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>The Borrower shall indemnify KFI against all losses, damages, costs and expenses whatsoever that may arise pursuant to this Agreement or as a result of non-fulfillment by the Borrower of any of the conditions of the Agreement.</td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.8	SEVERABILITY<b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>If any provision of the Agreement hereof shall be illegal or unenforceable for any reason the legality and enforceability of the remainder of the provisions of the Agreement shall not be affected or impaired thereby.</td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.9	OTHERS<b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>The Borrower’s liability hereunder shall not be affected, terminated or prejudiced by any amendments to or changes in the Borrower’s ownership or management or in its constitution, Memorandum or Articles of Association etc., by any winding-up, liquidation, reorganisation or any similar process or becoming bankrupt or insolvent or any proceeding in respect thereof or, any analogous step, but such liability shall continue in full force and effect and shall be binding on the Borrower’s respective successors.</td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.10	GOVERNING TERMS AND CONDITIONS</b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>The Borrower declares and confirms that the Facilities agreed to be granted to the Borrower shall be governed by the terms and conditions as set out in the Sanction Letter, this Agreement as well as those embodied in the relative security documents.</td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.11	RIGHT OF SET OFF AND LIEN	</b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>KFI at all times shall have the right of lien and set off and apply any and all assets, security, credits, money or properties of the Borrower in KFI’s possession or control against the obligation of the Borrower to KFI. 	That in addition to any general lien or similar right to which KFI may be entitled by law, KFI may at any time and without any notice to the Borrower combine or consolidate all or any of the Borrower’s accounts with KFI and liabilities to KFI and set off and transfer any sum or sums standing to the credit of any one or more such accounts in or towards the satisfaction of any of the Borrower’s liabilities to KFI on any other account or in any other respect, whether such liabilities be actual, contingent, primary or collateral and several or joint.It is agreed, acknowledged and understood that if the Borrower commits a default under this Agreement, the same shall be deemed to a default of all other facilities availed of by the Borrower, and notwithstanding any contrary elsewhere , KFI shall regard all borrowings of the Borrower as immediately due and payable and KFI shall be entitled to recall all the facilities granted to the Borrower and also utilize and enforce any mortgage, charge, pledge, hypothecation, lien, or any other security interest (“Security”) created and subsisting as on date towards recovery of its dues under the facilities. </td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.12	TERM OF THE AGREEMENT<b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>The Effective Date of this Agreement shall be as specified in Schedule I. The Agreement shall continue to subsist until terminated as per the terms contained herein.Notwithstanding anything contained herein, KFI may at any time in its discretion, serve not less than 7days written notice on the Borrower for termination of this Agreement. Termination shall not affect any rights or obligations which have accrued or arisen prior to the termination and shall not affect the applicability of the provisions of this Agreement to transactions which have taken place prior to the termination. Termination in any manner shall not affect the KFI’s security interest or the Borrower’s obligations to the KFI under this Agreement and other Transaction Documents.KFI reserves the right to revoke or cancel the Facilities and/ or vary, alter, modify or rescind, amend or change at any time any one or more of the terms and conditions of the facility at its discretion with such notice as KFI may deem reasonable and without assigning any reasons.The provision of the Facilities is at the total discretion of KFI and any request for extension/ enhancement / renewal of the Facilities and any disbursements thereunder will be at the discretion of KFI and on fulfillment of terms and conditions as prescribed by KFI.</td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'><b>13.13	DECLARATION BY THE BORROWER: <b></td>");
                sb.Append(@"</tr>");
                sb.Append(@"<tr>");
                sb.AppendFormat(@"<td width='100%' align='justify' style='font-family:Garamond,Geneva, sans-serif; font-size:16px; line-height:16px;'>The Borrower understands that as a pre-condition, relating to the grant of the Facility to the Borrower, KFI requires its/his/her consent for the disclosure by KFI of, information and data relating to the Borrower, of the credit facility availed of/to be availed, by the Borrower, obligations assumed or to be assumed by the Borrower in relation thereto and default, if any, committed by the Borrower, in discharge thereof. Accordingly, the Borrower hereby agrees and gives consent for the disclosure by KFI of all or any such (a) information and data relating to the Borrower (b) the information or data relating to any credit facility availed of/ to be availed (c) default, if any, committed by the Borrower in discharge of the Borrower’s obligations, as KFI may deem appropriate and necessary, to disclose and furnish the Credit Information Bureau (India) Ltd. (CIBIL) and/or any other agency authorized in this behalf by Reserve Bank of India. The Borrower undertakes and declares that CIBIL or any other agency so authorized may use, process the said information and data disclosed by KFI in the manner as deemed fit by them. Further CIBIL or any other agency so authorized may furnish for consideration, the processed information and data or products thereof prepared by them, to banks/financial institutions and other NBFC’s, credit grantors and registered users, as may be specified by the Reserve Bank of India in this behalf. The Borrower declares that the he/she/it’s authorized signatory is of sound mind and has understood the terms of this Agreement and undertakes to abide by them. The terms and conditions of the Agreement has been translated in a vernacular language as understood by the Borrower. </td>");
